These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, baseball, soccer
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, colombian, british
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, salsa, electronic
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, librarian, scientist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, family
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, apricot, fuchsia
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, november
 1. the person who likes apricot is the librarian##1
 2. the person watching adventure movies is not the firefighter##6
 3. the fan of blues is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the librarian is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is the fan of salsa##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 8. the british is not to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##8
 9. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the scientist##1
10. the british is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
11. the person who likes apricot is not the person watching animation movies##6
12. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5
13. the nigerian is in the middle##1
14. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |
| Sport      | soccer      | baseball  | handball |
| Nationality          | british  | nigerian      | colombian        |
| Music-Genre         | electronic     | salsa     | blues      |
| Job           | firefighter | librarian | scientist   |
| Movie-Genre   | family      | adventure | animation   |
| Color           | fuchsia  | apricot      | ebony      |
| Birthday     | march    | june   | november        |

